text: Kim Kardashian West. Evan Agostini / Invision / AP The INSIDER Summary : Paparazzi photos of Kim Kardashian West in a bikini on a Mexico beach surfaced online this April. A teaser for the next ` ` Keeping Up With the Kardashians'' episode shows Kim reacting to the photos. ` ` Oh my god,'' she said. ` ` I literally don't look like this!'' Some people body - shamed Kim's cellulite in April when the photos first appeared. Although Kim reacted with a body - positive tweet calling her body ` ` flawless,'' she later claimed on ` ` The View'' that the pictures were Photoshopped to look ` ` worse.''
